data.text:
Education:

Master of Science in Education (Counseling and Counselor Education), IUPUI

Bachelor of Science in Electrical Engineering, University of Notre Dame

Professional Experience:

How long in ACD?: Since September 2000

What do you like about the work you do?: Combining university knowledge and life experience to help students succeed

Past jobs/experiences:

Career consultant at IUPUI

Management and engineering positions at Ameritech/AT&T/Indiana Bell

Advice to students: Know why you are in college, what your strengths are, and what you want your future to be. Find an honest balance between what it takes for you to succeed academically and your other life needs.

If you could be any major in your cluster, what would it be? Why?: English. I love to read, write, and speak (and I think I am good at doing those things).
